have expressed interest in purchasing The San Francisco Examiner,
but only one was willing to say so. Failed mayoral candidate Clint
Reilly, who went to court last month to prevent The Examiner from
merging with the San Francisco Chronicle, has now emerged as a
potential buyer of the 135-year-old daily newspaper. By PETER
HARTLAUB.
