   AUSTRIA-INTELLECTUALS (Vienna) _ Vienna's large and active
community of artists, intellectuals, and dissidents have been
shaken by the ascent of Joerg Haider's far right party, but they
debate heatedly whether parallels with 1938-39 are apt, or wild
exaggerations. By Kevin Cullen. 1350 words. (i and e coding)
</P>
