   &UR; POLITICS (p) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   GOP-DEBATE-ANALYSIS (Columbia, S.C.) _ Amid heated charges and
countercharges, the stakes are huge for George W. Bush and John
McCain. By Michael Kranish. 1300 words.
</P>
