r d BC-GOURMET-LIST-TEX     02-16 0132
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-GOURMET-LIST-TEX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
WHAT IT TAKES FOR A GOURMET RAFTING TRIP
</HEADLINE>
 
(Accompanies BC-GOURMET-RAFTING) (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
c.2000 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
<P>
   Rafting trip food and dining provisions for 17 guests and 10
staff:
</P>
<P>
   _ 14 pounds Alaskan silver salmon fillets
</P>
<P>
   _ 7 pounds duck breasts
</P>
<P>
   _ 2 pounds smoked salmon
</P>
<P>
   _ 100 marinated jumbo shrimp
</P>
<P>
   _ 7 pounds rack of lamb
</P>
<P>
   _ 2 pounds truffle pate
</P>
<P>
   _ 2 pints cream
</P>
<P>
   _ 100 eggs
</P>
<P>
   _ 24 bottles white wine
