<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    SUMMIT SEEKS TO BOOST TRADE BETWEEN U.S., FRICA
 &HT;    (800&AMP;ADD)
 &HT;    With chart information attached at end of story.
