TransPoint, a venture between Microsoft and First Data. The deal
would make cHeckfree the monster in online billing and payment,
which is expected to get huge now that Y2K fears have come and
gone. Investors liked it, driving CKFR shares up 40 percent in the
first 30 minutes of trading Wednesday. (Clothier, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 20.
