   VULCAN-SPORTING-NEWS (Undated) _ Paul G. Allen, who co-founded
Microsoft with Bill Gates, announced Wednesday that his company,
Vulcan Ventures Inc., is buying The Sporting News, the country's
oldest sporting magazine, from Times Mirror Co. By Alex Kuczynski.
</P>
<P>
   (Scheduled to move by 9 p.m. ET.)
</P>
