rising cost of home heating oil. Clinton, at his first official
news conference of the year, says the money, which would come out
of the Low Income Home Energy Assistance Program (LIHEAP), is all
that is left this year in the government fund that aids those who
must rely on oil to heat their homes. By MARK HELM. (Already
filed.)
