<TEXT>
<P>
   &QL;  NEVADA SEED CO.'S BANKRUPTCY HEIGHTENS FARM CRISIS By Sara
Barnett
</P>
<P>
   States News Service
</P>
<P>
   WASHINGTON, Feb.16 - The seed-supply company that once prided
itself on keeping the White House lawn green is in the red. When
