   BILL BRADLEY Boston, Dorchester, Mass.; Providence, R.I.; Old
Saybrook, New Haven, Conn.; and Purchase, N.Y.
</P>
<P>
   GEORGE W. BUSH Florence, Conway, Litchfield and Charleston, S.C.
</P>
<P>
   AL GORE Bridge City, La.; New Orleans; Jackson, Miss., and
Washington
</P>
