<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-02-16 23:46 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9493 &Cx1f; taf-z
u s BC-SKI-BLACK-RACERS-NYT &LR;      02-16 0725
